files.description: Full EHI Export documentation page — Word-to-HTML document containing purpose statement, export format description (CSV + C-CDA + PDF), assumptions, and data dictionary (as embedded images). Last updated 11/28/2023.
Screenshot of TechCare UI showing the EHI export notification message with 'All Facilities' dropdown and Messages badge.
Data dictionary: Demographics table — 10 fields including ID, Booking Number, BookingDate, CustodyStatus, First/Last Name, DOB, Gender, HousingLocation, SSN.
Data dictionary: Medications table — ~22 fields including drug description, SIG instructions, start/stop dates, GPI, route, order type, quantity, refills, authorizing provider NPI.
Data dictionary: Allergies table — ~14 fields including allergy name/type, onset/stop dates, NDC, allergy class, GPI, reaction description (SNOMED).
Data dictionary: Problem List table — ~10 fields including ICD-10 code, problem name (from FLAGS), date identified/resolved, resolve text.
Data dictionary: Flags (alerts) table — ~8 fields including subject, message, alert date, location ID.
Data dictionary: Appointments table — ~13 fields including scheduled/completed dates, appointment type, status, housing location, reason, created by.
Data dictionary: Diet Orders table — ~12 fields including diet type code/description, status, order/end dates, clinical comments, cancel reason.
Data dictionary: Lab Orders table — ~14 fields including order code (lab type), test name, status, order/end dates, service provider, priority.
Data dictionary: Treatment Orders table — ~12 fields including treatment code, description (free text), status, order/end dates, clinical comments.
Data dictionary: Specialty Consult Orders table — ~13 fields including order code (offsite/onsite/hospitalization/ER), specialty type, status, priority.
Data dictionary: Admission Orders table — ~12 fields including admission management type, order description, status, order/end dates, clinical comments (quick notes).
Data dictionary: Immunizations table — ~22 fields including CVX code, vaccine name, manufacturer (MVX), lot number, route, site, VIS info, refusal reasons. Most detailed table in the dictionary.
